com.ibm.team.process.client

Interface IAdvisorProblemResolution


  • public interface IAdvisorProblemResolution
    An executable resolution for an advisor problem. Resolutions are performed by contributed delegates, which are instantiated lazily to avoid plug-in loading.

    This interface may not be implemented by clients.

    Since:
    0.7
